{"tid":1469600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好唔記得要遣責AA","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:24:52.000Z","uid":23071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6079db3108e9992a4c324836c33482b4667e5b","tid":1469600,"uid":23071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"如來尋日唔少經機管局公布取消/DELAY既航班, 最終如期起飛/冇DELAY(平時搭開遲15分鐘30分鐘果D都當埋準時). 目的係想將件事變為 &quot;乘客上唔到機係因為到禁區入口比示威人士阻塞&quot; 將件事由好似星期一所有人指責AA同埋航空公司取消晒D機, 轉為指向示威者既責任.<br />\n<br />\n因為最終D飛機確實如期飛左, 除非當時有screen cap機管局app或者影低機場航班布告版, 否則紀錄上唔會知道原來發生過咁既事.<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇到金水page都有人講左:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.503741983045963/2385141034906039/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fphotos%2Fa.503741983045963%2F2385141034906039%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0T%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=e4532d73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/a.503741983045963/2385141034906039/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/pcb.2385054158248060/2385054094914733/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.2385054158248060%2F2385054094914733%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0T%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=4b9294dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/photos/pcb.2385054158248060/2385054094914733/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n同聯合國人權委員會要求調查警察涉嫌違反人權單野一齊推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1462257/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1462257/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9d8af81ebfec471858088b9d743d0236f3152b47","tid":1469600,"uid":23071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bea1ebaa2a7b99aff8d98505c34e7f627151640e","ti